INSTALL

1) Place the contents of the /AutoSubscribe/ folder in your web root
2) Edit the config.inc file and insert your icontact login information, the mailing list ID that you want to subscribe contacts to and API key 


For Joomla: 
3) Point your cron script to /AutoSubscribe/Joomla.php



To get your API key from iContact visit this page:
http://developer.icontact.com/documentation/register-and-enable-your-application

To get your mailing ID number, just log into your account and view the mailing list.  In the URL will be the mailing ID